---
// OUR 5 STEP PROCESS Section
// Removed Card component wrapper - unnecessary complexity
// Improved mobile layout - cards breathe better
---

<section id="difference" class="mb-5 rounded-2xl bg-white px-4 py-16 sm:px-6">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl">
    <!-- Top grid: headline + stats -->
    <div class="mb-12 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-ink mb-4 text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight">
          We don't aim for average. <br />We're engineered for excellence.
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="text-ink space-y-2">
        <p>95% of people who lose weight gain it all back</p>
        <p>Because they stop when the number on the.</p>
        <p>We don't stop there.</p>
        <p>
          We hardwire the habits, mindset, and environment it takes to never go
          back.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 5 Step Process -->
    <div class="mt-16">
      <h3 class="text-ink mb-5 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">
        OUR 5 STEP PROCESS
      </h3>
      <p class="text-ink mb-8">
        Our formula is based in science that produces a mathematical certainty
        via the MED (Minimal Effective Dose).
      </p>

      <!-- Cards grid -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-5">
        <div
          class="bg-surface-dark text-ink-dark flex aspect-square flex-col items-center justify-center rounded-2xl p-8"
        >
          <p class="mb-6 text-6xl font-bold md:text-7xl">1</p>
          <div class="text-center">
            <p class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase">STRIP</p>
            <p class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase">
              THE FAT
            </p>
            <br />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div
          class="bg-surface-dark text-ink-dark flex aspect-square flex-col items-center justify-center rounded-2xl p-8"
        >
          <p class="mb-6 text-6xl font-bold md:text-7xl">2</p>
          <div class="text-center">
            <p class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase">EAT</p>
            <p class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase">
              PURPOSELY
            </p>
            <br />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div
          class="bg-surface-dark text-ink-dark flex aspect-square flex-col items-center justify-center rounded-2xl p-8"
        >
          <p class="mb-6 text-6xl font-bold md:text-7xl">3</p>
          <div class="text-center">
            <p class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase">
              HYDRATE
            </p>
            <p class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase">
              HYDRATE. HYDRATE
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div
          class="bg-surface-dark text-ink-dark flex aspect-square flex-col items-center justify-center rounded-2xl p-8"
        >
          <p class="mb-6 text-6xl font-bold md:text-7xl">4</p>
          <div class="text-center">
            <p class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase">
              LOCK IN
            </p>
            <p class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase">STEPS</p>
            <br />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div
          class="bg-surface-dark text-ink-dark flex aspect-square flex-col items-center justify-center rounded-2xl p-8"
        >
          <p class="mb-6 text-6xl font-bold md:text-7xl">5</p>
          <div class="text-center">
            <p class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase">
              TRAIN SMARTER
            </p>
            <p class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase">
              NOT HARDER
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
